INSERT INTO peer_repo_subscriptions
                (peer_instance_id, repository_id, sync_enabled, replication_mode, replication_schedule)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
            ON CONFLICT (peer_instance_id, repository_id) DO UPDATE SET
                sync_enabled = $3,
                replication_mode = $4,
                replication_schedule = $5
